For Mexico relations with the United States - heavy and full of old grudges question.
Most Americans have never thought about that, in 1848, the United States invaded Mexico and under the gun rifles forced its leaders to abandon half of its territory.
But the Mexicans think for centuries, not minutes, and see the reminder of the events in all.
Therefore it is only any statesman us understand one word of criticism in the direction of Mexico, in the press and among the elite of the Mexican society immediately hear complaints about the fact that Americans infringe on the sovereignty of neighbors.
And the descendants of Montezuma преисполняются militancy.
The most complex is the relationship of Mexico with more than 35 million Americans of Mexican origin living in the United States.
Want to talk about insults?
Enough of them.
In Mexico there are winners and losers, people, who find in this country for themselves of the opportunity, and those for whom there is no such possibility.
In Los Angeles, Las Vegas, Phoenix, Denver and San-Antonio so many people of Mexican origin for one reason only: at some point in their family history who-either the father or grandfather had no opportunity to realize themselves in Mexico and was forced to go to the North.
More often it was the Mexicans of a certain type - dark, poorly educated, from a poor peasant families.
We are their descendants, and we remember this.
In Mexico, see it differently.
Today our life is an embodiment of the American dream, we were in good schools and settled on the good work, but we should not forget the fact that even this dream is the American, not Mexican.
Our national self-determination of confusing and it is not clear, but we know which country consider their own.
The United States Of America.
